18
00:02:08,094 --> 00:02:10,330
Wait, it was Ko Mi-nam?

19
00:02:19,606 --> 00:02:21,374
Darn it. Come on!

20
00:02:46,299 --> 00:02:47,834
Did I hear it correctly?

21
