Forget it, Ko Mi-nam.

53
00:06:37,630 --> 00:06:38,464
Just say no!

54
00:06:38,831 --> 00:06:39,699
No.

55
00:06:39,866 --> 00:06:41,267
I can't be all arrogant like him.

56
00:06:42,301 --> 00:06:44,437
