between me, Shin-woo, and Jermy.

113
00:10:10,209 --> 00:10:11,310
A love triangle?

114
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:27,460
Shin-woo?

115
00:10:34,133 --> 00:10:34,967
Jermy.

116
00:10:35,768 --> 00:10:38,704
You don't see anyone else but Shin-woo.

117
00:10:54,353 --> 00:10:55,187
