119
00:11:07,266 --> 00:11:08,100
You two!

120
00:11:09,568 --> 00:11:10,536
I'll get my revenge.

121
00:11:18,644 --> 00:11:20,179
"I'll get my revenge!"

122
00:11:21,247 --> 00:11:22,081
Wow.

123
00:11:22,581 --> 00:11:23,716
Shin-woo finally

124
