131
00:11:46,872 --> 00:11:48,307
Jermy's cutest ever ending song!

132
00:11:48,641 --> 00:11:49,975
Okay, I will.

133
00:12:02,488 --> 00:12:05,524
I hope Ko Mi-nam smiles like you
after she hears my song.

134
00:12:20,372 --> 00:12:22,108
