201
00:18:18,497 --> 00:18:19,865
How am I supposed to be okay with that?

202
00:18:21,967 --> 00:18:22,801
Why?

203
00:18:24,069 --> 00:18:25,337
Why isn't it me?

204
00:18:27,606 --> 00:18:30,075
